Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please... I want you to come back to me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.21,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't do this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not being able to keep our promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.84,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:22.93,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:28.90,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:36.28,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.99,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:46.91,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:55.80,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:02:00.72,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:07.85,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:14.61,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.84,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.80,0:01:22.93,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.93,0:01:28.90,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:36.28,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.99,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:46.91,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:55.80,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:02:00.72,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:07.85,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:14.61,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:28.96,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,960)\pos(160,381)\fscx112.5\fscy103.75}Episode 13 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class won the basketball tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me? I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... there he goes with his popularity again. Are you okay with this, Nana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, hey. Next up is the boy's bullet finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We totally have to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, why did you break up with Yano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.54,0:03:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bugging the hell out of me, so spill already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard so many rumors that it's starting to drive me nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rumors...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you wouldn't let him do you, which pushed Yano to the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...where he couldn't deal with it anymore, so he lost his patience and fell out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds pretty reasonable to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's the true story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry, Mizu-chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean... you loved him so much.\NI guess things like this wear out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here's a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return it once you're done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And feel free to give it back just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since we broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned the manga and CDs I borrowed from him, as well as a mechanical pencil I had taken without him noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I might find the girl manga I forced on him in my cubby the next day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it still hasn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even look at each other in class anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the way things are going...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're slowly becoming strangers, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was definitely a two-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it could be. I can't think of any other reason he'd be dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible. If he was cheating on her, she'd hate him so much that she'd want him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I think he was cheating, too. Though it was mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l Nana must've had it really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Li'l Nana"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separate classifications! Li'l Nana and Stupid Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna come see something nice later?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were left in front of my house a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's so mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for someone to take care of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about at your house, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... my parents hate pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do much about that. I guess I'll have to raise them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have much choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just abandon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be fate that they came to my house. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's licking my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've laughed before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean like you just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's important to make time to just forget everything and laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun just stays by my side without asking a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come over to see them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever get lonely, come on over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm not really implying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Takeuchi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bye then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hook-up party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, on Saturday. I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry... I can't make it. I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around like that. I got a lot of girls by promising you'd be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little bastard... you never planned to go, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know, it's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the 49 days of mourning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It still hasn't passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about going with something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying things like that to make people feel pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things like that don't suit you. Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This riverbed's kinda nice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's invite some friends, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and could you hide your face with glasses or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You really don't have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long has it been since you've had one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:37.03,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to hide face, not to stand out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he just got dumped. You better go easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just dumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you break up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares? Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we hurt your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when's your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,July.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... so you're more sensitive than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a fortune teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I happened to see your cell phone before, and it looked like the same model as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Only the color's different, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His background is still the girlfriend he broke up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see, lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kinda plain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I thought he would've been going out with someone cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Yano-kun doesn't care about looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Shouldn't they be calling her "really cute" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. It's just a pain to change, which is why it's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll change it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also erase this old picture, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I erased it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.93,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(527,80)\fscx288.75\fscy236.25\b1\c&HBDA38A&\frz332.49}Shocked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now connecting you to voicemail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi, do you still have that picture of Takahashi in her yukata that you sent to me a year ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, send it to me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure. Actually, I'm kinda sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna make like a tree and... you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I'm broke today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, so we're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? You want to spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's with you, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really no good if I'm not with the girl I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Takahashi's picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have that old thing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... it's 02:30. Get out of here. Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.62,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Take!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're secretly hiding that picture from me, I won't get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just please send it to me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would be fun about having a picture of someone else's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Look for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girls I met today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They called Takahashi ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said she was "plain."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her being plain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... let me sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi's a hundred times cuter than those arrogant, unsympathetic, "delicate" bitches...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who drench themselves in makeup. Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, correction... I meant a thousand times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's cuter, her or Nana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with all of you? Every single one of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try bringing them together and lining them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try lining both of them up in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who I'd pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do if I went out with Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that you have no right to complain if she finds another guy while you idle around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all... love is all about timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say the right thing at the right moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter how much fate was involved in the relationship, everything will be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you regret it, it'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you regret it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the money I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that arrogant little boy's name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Moto. Could you give this back to him and say thanks from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? We didn't give this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:14:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 220 yen here. That's 80 yen more than what we gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On, it's fine. It's just 80 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's small change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fine. Whether it's 80 or 800,000 yen, money is still money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's even things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shoot... nothing but junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that key for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my bike key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50... 60... oh, I'm 20 yen short.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This caramel should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? I can see my breath here in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, how did he get in last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I won't forget to lock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll actually get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in the middle of writing a message?
