Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:15:04.92,arrow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\frz3.725\c&H9C8D61&\b1\fscx191.25\fscy260\frx358\fry2\pos(192,112)}Takahashi,\N I never thought\N of you as a\N replacement for\N her. None of my\N feelings have been\N false.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi, I never thought of you as a replacement for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of my feelings have been false.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I regret what I did so much that I want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... back at that place... those actions I took...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I choose to say is always wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
