Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.61,arrow,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b1\fscx57.5\fscy117.5\frx356\fry14\frz4.177\pos(213,360)}{\p1\c&H9C8D61&}m 10 -11 l 10 -11 l 10 44 l 42 44 l 42 -11{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:43.79,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&H878469&\fscx63.75\fscy70\frx14\fry328\frz28.74\pos(433,327)}Before\NHigh School
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you took my futon, I caught a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to worry like this, you should hurry up and say what needs to be said already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare touch Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and tell Takahashi that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you'll be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun, can I come to see the puppies again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought something for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think this is cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard puppies like plush toys, so I brought some from my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I have other plans today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I must be an annoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... but you can go see them even if I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... maybe some other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm just the ex of one of his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:14.18,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko ni itemo donna toki mo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:20.06,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga kieta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:27.98,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kesenai omoide nokoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.36,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Uketomeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:39.49,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomadoi wa itsuka fukai umi de
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:45.16,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Aoi suna ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:53.55,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Samenai omoi issho ni
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.93,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono you na no darou
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:05.60,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga inai kono beddo de
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:10.69,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori yureteiru
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:22.79,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Negaeri wo uttara aozora ga mieta
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:14.18,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere, anytime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.18,0:17:20.06,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept the unreasonable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:27.98,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,left behind since the day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:32.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:39.49,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,This bewilderment will become blue sand
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:45.16,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,deep in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:53.55,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if these unrelenting feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:57.93,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,will be just like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:05.60,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quivering alone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:10.69,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,in this bed without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:22.79,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I rolled over, I couldn't see the blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I suddenly have all this time to myself again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an empty hole has formed inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I notice the things I forgot to give back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The memories of Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hateful Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Childish Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teasing Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet Yano...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything Yano left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to not rely on people so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and move forward.
