Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... I'd like to start discussing what sort of float we'll have in the Culture Festival this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class didn't win anything last year, so we have to win this year, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, going by what won last year...
