Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:19:03.62,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad300,0)\pos(511,115)\c&HFFFFFF&}Elephant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:19:03.62,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad300,0)\pos(505,143)\c&HFFFFFF&}Pyramid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:19:03.62,tab.,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad300,0)\pos(527,172)\c&HFFFFFF&}NORA Rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.77,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of these are any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you guys do anything but cut corners with circles, triangles and white things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to at least clear our sucky name from not even making 3rd place last year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there more meaning in just being able to participate...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that half-assed crap! We're gonna win this year, no matter what! Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have any ideas for a style filled with our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has plenty of color...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...something vivid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that'll surprise anyone who sees it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean, filled with our dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us an example?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? An example? Umm, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:27.39,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\frz270\fscx273.75\fscy160\pos(455,235)\c&HFFFFFF&}Plenty of color...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.39,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\frz270\fscx207.5\fscy141.25\pos(457,242)\c&HFFFFFF&}Filled with our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:31.64,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\frz270\fscx331.25\fscy127.5\pos(459,235)\c&HFFFFFF&}Vivid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plenty of color...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like a peacock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filled with our dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A rainbow? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... it's pretty difficult to come up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A peacock?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said a rainbow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does anyone have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, great! Who's going to suggest something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah... Ya-Yano-kun. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Disneyland?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could build the castle, use that mouse character, and light it up with decorative bulbs and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it were Tokyo Disneyland, it would be even better!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.66,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&}Sign: Nora Rabbit, Disney Land, It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.53,0:20:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idea for Disneyland was really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really helped me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spoke to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going to the student council meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see Yano's eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... don't confuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:16.96,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H817D5D&\frx24\fry26\frz342.883\move(162,507,163,143,0,3282)}Before\N High School
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, mind if we stop by the plaza?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long-sleeved T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana, where are you off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I think I might wanna get a bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bag? That'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go to that store in front of the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:50.12,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H817D5D&\b1\fscx172.5\fscy130\pos(93,198)}Before\N High School{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here's the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd I put my pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto, I just remembered some things I need to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you my final notice this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.06,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all about timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come see them again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hold back anymore!
