Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:44.92,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like the seasons have changed slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.92,0:22:52.81,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sunbeams have thinned and will one day shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:23:01.81,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was relieved, knowing our bus
