Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:17.75,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You always gaze up to me from outside my window
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.26,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I mimic you by doing the same
